<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Rustplats details capitalisation award.</title>
<headline>Rustplats details capitalisation award.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1997-02-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>Rustenburg Platinum Holdings Ltd said on Monday it would offer capitalisation shares on the basis of the ratio that 52.5 cents bears to the average share price in the three days to March 26.</p>
<p>Registration date for the issue is February 28. Shareholders may elect to receive an interim cash dividend of 50 cents instead.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
